 class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532683\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532683\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 21, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104uhg1665702743762.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uhg1665702743762.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uhg1665702743762.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uhg1665702743762\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"uhg1665702743762__userunprefix_481283\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies whether the WRD should handle references to documents on relative paths\n      (such as <span class=\"ph filepath\">../css/applic.css</span>).</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"uhg1665702743762__topic_d147635e1_d147636e1_d147637e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uhg1665702743762__p_d147638e1_d147639e1_d147640e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;init-param&gt; </code></p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;param-name&gt;</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">UseRunPrefix</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/param-name&gt; </code></p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;param-value&gt;</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">TRUE</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">FALSE</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/param-value&gt; </code></p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/init-param&gt;</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uhg1665702743762__p_d147641e1_d147642e1_d147643e1\">Default value if omitted: <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uhg1665702743762__topic_d106432e1_d106433e1_d106434e1_d106435e1_d106436e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1022670e97\">Values</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uhg1665702743762__li_d51239e1_d51240e1_d51241e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">TRUE</code>—the WRD Java servlet redirects a request, for example\n                  <span class=\"ph filepath\">css/applic.css</span>, to the root of the WRD servlet, or to the\n               value of the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">WEBAPPURL</span> setting.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uhg1665702743762__li_d51242e1_d51243e1_d51244e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uhg1665702743762__p_d147647e1_d147648e1_d147649e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>—the WRD will not process relative paths starting with <span class=\"ph filepath\">../</span>, because the URL-pattern does not match. Therefore, the presence of relative paths, such as <span class=\"ph filepath\">../css/applic.css</span>, will not cause errors.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uhg1665702743762__p_d147650e1_d147651e1_d147652e1\">The value of the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">WEBAPPURL</span> setting is not used.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uhg1665702743762__p_d147653e1_d147654e1_d147655e1\">If an existing URL contains the <code class=\"ph codeph\">/run</code> prefix, it is redirected a URL without the prefix.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uhg1665702743762__p_d147656e1_d147657e1_d147658e1\">For example,\n                     <code class=\"ph codeph\">http://urltowebserver/uniface/wrd/run/logonusp.start</code> is\n                  redirected to\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">http://urltowebserver/uniface/wrd/logonusp.start</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vkl1665702743832.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>WEBAPPURL</a><p>Specifies the absolute URL path of the web application directory for the WRD Java servlet.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532683\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532683\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UseRunPrefix Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 21, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies whether the WRD should handle references to documents on relative paths (such as ../css/applic.css ). <init-param> <param-name> UseRunPrefix </param-name> <param-value> TRUE | FALSE </param-value> </init-param> Default value if omitted: True . Values TRUE —the WRD Java servlet redirects a request, for example css/applic.css , to the root of the WRD servlet, or to the value of the WEBAPPURL setting. False —the WRD will not process relative paths starting with ../ , because the URL-pattern does not match. Therefore, the presence of relative paths, such as ../css/applic.css , will not cause errors. The value of the WEBAPPURL setting is not used. If an existing URL contains the /run prefix, it is redirected a URL without the prefix. For example, http://urltowebserver/uniface/wrd/run/logonusp.start is redirected to http://urltowebserver/uniface/wrd/logonusp.start Related Links WEBAPPURL Specifies the absolute URL path of the web application directory for the WRD Java servlet. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}